2026-04-28T07:30:06.3412960Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-28T07:30:06.3413752Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-28T07:30:06.3414728Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-28T07:30:06.3415452Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
